Titolo: Outcast (video game)

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: Outcast is an action-adventure video game developed by Belgian developer Appeal and released by Infogrames for Windows in 1999. The game was critically acclaimed and was named the "Adventure Game of the Year" by GameSpot in 1999. In 2001, Appeal developed a sequel, called Outcast II: The Lost Paradise, which was never finished due to bankruptcy. In 2010, the game was re-released via digital distribution on GOG. In 2014, Outcast was remastered as Outcast 1.1, after the original developers reacquired the franchise IP. In 2017, a remake titled Outcast: Second Contact was released for Windows, PlayStation 4, and Xbox One.
In 2021, THQ Nordic announced an official sequel titled Outcast 2: A New Beginning, the game is being developed by Appeal and scheduled to be released for Windows, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X/S.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
